Compact and cleaning is a breeze - unlike large units which are a hassle to store and clean, our pocket-sized spiralizer fits just about anywhere! The spiralizer can be fully disassembled with ease and every component is dishwasher-safe.


Functionality with ease - 4 options to fulfil all of your spiralizing needs in 1 space-saving kitchen gadget. Perfect for zoodles, healthy vegetable pastas and gorgeous garnishes and all available with just an easy push of a button.


Mess-free storage solutions- the Fullstar spiralizer comes with a removable container to catch all of your freshly sliced veg and lid so you have the option to store it for later.


Keeping you and your family safe - we know our stainless steel blades are high quality and razor sharp. Our handheld spiralizer therefore comes with a non-slip fingerguard to keep you safe whilst in use. This also minimises waste and maximise your yield of delicious zoodles.


Read the manual carefully - Please read the instruction manual provided with the Fullstar vegetable spiralizer closely before use. If you have any questions or issues regarding the spiralizer please do not hesitate to send the seller a message through Amazon and we will respond within 24 hours

Kiss Your Blues Away: Blue spirulina powder meets adaptogens, lemon balm, passion flower & blueberry to create a superfood powder to calm the mind and body. Replace supplements with a blend that has a mood boost & immune system booster.


Stress Relief: Ashwagandha & reishi are adaptogens that help reduce cortisol levels, providing stress and calming + natural energy. Passion flower & lemon balm are also natural alternatives to pills, aiding with sleep & mood support.


Mental Clarity: Lemon balm is a mood booster and focus supplement that helps clear brain fog with GABA, a neurotransmitter that supports memory & cognition. No memory pills needed. The B vitamins in PANMOL B-complex offer an extra brain boost.


Immunity Booster: Organic spirulina is packed with beta carotene, vitamin B & iron for powerful immune support. Its chlorophyll also supports digestion health. Blueberry powder adds its anti-inflammatory properties into the immune booster mix, too!


Out of the Blue: If you want a complementary energy booster, check out our electric boostberry flavored energizing blend with organic blue spirulina powder, cordyceps, rhodiola, ginseng & more! 70mg caffeine & only 20 cal + 1g sugar per serving.

SOFT AND STYLISH - This is the softest shirt you will ever wear. It features an amazingly cool and soft feel. Say goodbye to those itchy and scratchy shirts from the old days. This piece of apparel will keep you looking stylish and hip. Speaking of stylish, these make a great gift for any day. Who wouldn't love this as a gift on Christmas, Father's Day, Mother's Day, Valentine's Day, Boss's Day, or even a Birthday!


GREAT QUALITY AND DURABLE - Our t-shirt's quality is top notch. It features 100% cotton at a weight of 6oz for a nice solid feel. Durable you ask? Well yes it is! It features double-needle stitching throughout as well as a taped shoulder-to-shoulder hem for a strong construction base. Lastly, its seamless collar makes sure you are totally comfortable in it. This shirt definitely won't fall apart in the wash and it feels like a hug as you wearing it.


THE PRINT - These are printed with care upon ordering. We've been doing this for a while so we have honed our skills and you will get the finest t-shirt we can offer you. The design you see is printed on the front centered chest, just like shown. Fear not. We've thought of everything with this product.


WHERE IS IT MADE? - Although the shirt itself may have been milled in multiple countries, a thorough inspection is done here in the USA. Once approved your item is printed by our trained staff and shipped directly to you right from the Good ol' USA. We take care in our craftsmanship and quality and will only deliver you a premium quality product.


WHAT SIZE IS IT? - Remember when Mom used to ask you if you had enough room in the crotch for your pants? Well this is no different. Make sure you reference our size chart graphic to make sure you have enough room in your armpit area. Nothing worse than ordering a shirt that is too small or too big. We recommend measuring a shirt you already own and comparing the dimensions to our graphic to guarantee you a perfect fit.

WHAT IT'S MADE OF - This women's v-neck is made from 100% combed ring spun cotton giving it the softest feel you've ever felt. If you are not aware, when cotton is combed and ring spun it gives it a much softer feel than a traditional cotton t-shirt. A lot of care and effort was put into finding the highest quality cotton and mill to manufacture this v-neck and we are proud to present it to you.


WHAT IT FEELS LIKE - This shirt has a weight of 4.2oz which gives it a nice light feel but not to the point of being too thin. This v-neck feels like a typical women's sizing but with the added comfort of ring spun cotton, it is so much better. As mentioned above, the ring spun cotton feels amazingly soft and comfortable. You won't feel any itch from this v-neck.


WHY YOU SHOULD BUY THIS - This v-neck makes a great gift for any gift giving holiday such as Mother's Day, Valentine's Day, Christmas, and even a Birthday. Of course you could purchase it for your own closet. There is no harm in buying things for yourself every once in a while.


WHAT THE SIZING IS LIKE - Although the sizing of this item appears to be standard, we always recommend checking our size chart graphic provided in the product images prior to purchase. If you have a favorite v-neck already we recommend measuring it and comparing it to the measurements in our size chart to make sure you're getting the best fit.

A PIECE OF HISTORY – Each photo from IMS is an original editorial photograph with certified authenticity and provenance. All photos were intended for editorial use, to help to depict those iconic moments that made history what we know it today. Each one represents a moment in history and makes a great addition to any collection. A true gem for all the history lovers out there!


All vintage photos are UNIQUE COLLECTIBLES/MEMORABILIA because there is only one of each item with such stamps, date, and hand-written scribbles in the backside. These marks attest and increase the value of the collectible. The watermark is not on the actual photo


The photos can also become the perfect WALL DECOR or A PERSONAL GIFT because of their uniqueness and minimalistic style. By adorning your home with them, it will feel like you are creating your personal private art gallery. All photos are ready for you to frame. Here at IMS Vintage Photos we recommend two-sided glass frames so that you can also display the back and show off your collectible


If you are building a family tree, this is the moment for you to FIND YOUR ROOTS: all these vintage photos were kept locked in archives for years until we came in, digitized them, and made them available to the public. Some of our clients have found historic photos of their family members during wars, award-winning ceremonies, and other newsworthy events


All photos from IMS are an INVESTMENT, in fact, the price and value of vintage photographs will increase in the future and might be the next valuable items of our times. Vintage press photographs are certainly not growing in numbers as they stopped making them after 1995. Many have been lost due to fires or water damages already. Take good care of your IMS vintage photograph as it might become even more valuable in the future
